query: select c.id,c.salutation,c.number, c.billing_address_id, a.recipient, a.address_line, a.address_extra, a.postal, a.country, c.delivery_address_id, a2.recipient, a2.address_line, a2.address_extra, a2.postal, a2.country from customer c inner join address a on c.billing_address_id = a.id left join address a2 on c.delivery_address_id = a2.id ;
